response.overview: Delightful Asian Treats! Dirty Debutantes vol. 111 hits the mark in an ALL-ASIAN feature! Kamiko Taka makes her first video with eagerness and class. Sexy Kami Boh teams up with lovely Malia, who starts off with a sexy dance. These two make a real fine pair! Sunni Nova makes her debut here, and although she looks shy, she's a real firecracker! Adorable Lisa Yung experiences her first time on camera as a way of satisfying her intense curiousity with all things sexual. Enjoy! Love, Ed. Starring; Lisa Yung, Kamiki Taka, Kami Boh, Malia, Sunni Nova, Ed Powrs.
response.title: More Dirty Debutantes 111
